Well i went with a friend and it was nice. i dance alot. lol yes me danced i did and i did gooooooooooooood! [or so i say i did] and nope i didn't ask the guy i liked for a dance. [This conversation was taken couple days before THE NITE] He said it was going to be a early night for him and his date at prom. :-\ i wanted a dance, me and my date didnt get there till like 9 p.m. and it started like 7p.m. So yeah we were fashionably late. And i saw him there... yep he was danceing amazing wow i didnt think he would. well i dont think he saw me or if he did he didnt come to say hi. i was going to come over where he was at and steal him away to boogy down on the dance floor,  nope no gutts in me but also i couldnt find him when i got the nerve to embarrass myself. "GD he came with a date, so  why would he dance with me that would be a diss to the chick i wouldnt want to cause trouble"...Well i've got to get over it i blew my chance if there even was one. Hes a senior its the end of school and i doubt i'll be seeing him at all.
